      <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed text-gray-300 mb-8">Every Scrabble game starts with the same 100 tiles, but not all letters are created equal. Understanding how tiles are distributed — which letters appear frequently and which are rare — gives you a strategic edge in rack management, tile tracking, and predicting your opponent's plays. Here's the complete breakdown.</p>

      <h2 class="text-xl font-light text-blue-400 mt-10 mb-4 border-l-4 border-blue-400 pl-4">Complete Tile Distribution</h2>
